## 🏗️ Proje Mimarisi

### Mimari Tasarım:

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Client["🖥️ Client Layer"]
        Browser["Web Browser"]
    end
    
    subgraph Frontend["⚛️ Frontend Container"]
        Vite["Vite Dev Server :5173"]
        Router["Custom Router"]
        Pages["Pages (TS)"]
        Services["API Services"]
    end
    
    subgraph Backend["🔧 Backend Container"]
        Fastify["Fastify Server :3000"]
        Controllers["Controllers"]
        Routes["Routes"]
        Middleware["JWT Middleware"]
        Prisma["Prisma ORM"]
        Studio["Prisma Studio :5555"]
    end
    
    subgraph Database["💾 Database"]
        SQLite["SQLite (dev.db)"]
    end
    
    subgraph External["🌐 External Services"]
        OAuth["42 OAuth API"]
    end
    
    Browser --> Vite
    Vite --> Router
    Router --> Pages
    Pages --> Services
    Services -->|HTTP/REST| Fastify
    Fastify --> Routes
    Routes --> Controllers
    Controllers --> Prisma
    Prisma --> SQLite
    Studio --> SQLite
    Controllers -->|OAuth Flow| OAuth
```

### Request Flow Örneği (Login):

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Kullanıcı
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as Database
    
    U->>F: Email/Password girer
    F->>B: POST /auth/login
    B->>DB: User bilgilerini sorgula
    DB-->>B: User verisi
    B->>B: Şifre doğrulama (bcrypt)
    alt 2FA Aktif
        B-->>F: {requires2FA: true}
        F->>U: 2FA kodu iste
        U->>F: 6 haneli kod girer
        F->>B: POST /auth/verify-2fa
        B->>B: TOTP doğrulama
    end
    B->>B: JWT token oluştur
    B-->>F: {token, user}
    F->>F: localStorage'a kaydet
    F-->>U: Dashboard'a yönlendir
```

